                "labels": [
                    {
                        "purpose": "M+ Sigg Collection",
                        "text": "In this photograph, Zheng Guogu and a dishevelled homeless young man are shown laughing while squatting on the street. It is part of a project where the artist befriended the mentally unstable man in his hometown Yangjiang. After following him for a period of time, he came to regard the marginalised man as a teacher."
                    },
                    {
                        "purpose": "Sigg Online",
                        "text": "In this photograph, Zheng Guogu and a young, dishevelled homeless man are shown laughing while squatting in the street. It is part of a project in which the artist befriended the mentally ill man in his hometown of Yangjiang. After following him for a period of time, he came to regard the marginalised man as a teacher."
                    }
                ]
            },
            "zh-hant": {
                "purposes": [
                    "M+ Sigg Collection",
                    "Sigg Online"
                ],
                "labels": [
                    {
                        "purpose": "M+ Sigg Collection",
                        "text": "這張照片紀錄了鄭國谷與一名頭髮凌亂的年輕男子蹲在街上歡笑的景象。作為藝術項目的一部分，鄭國谷在陽江與這位有精神障礙的露宿者結成好友，並跟隨他一段時間。經過溝通互動，鄭國谷視該社會邊緣人士為自己的老師。"
                    },
                    {
